{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

This template is used internally by [[Template:Flag]]. It is '''not''' intended to be transcluded directly. It provides the formatting for placing a small flag next to a country name.

See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Flag Template]] for further information.

